text.text:
I recently had the pleasure of visiting Harat Ward  with my family, and I must say, I'm not quite sure where to begin describing our wonderful experience. From the moment we walked in, we were drawn in by the inviting atmosphere and setting the perfect tone for our meal.

Our order included  Dynamite chicken pizza and peach ice tea. To our delight, every dish we tried was nothing short of amazing. Even though we took a safer option of the pizza, we would love to come again and try their authentic food.

A special shout-out goes to our waiter who suggested the peach ice tea. It was refreshing.

The staff were not only friendly but also incredibly attentive throughout our visit, ensuring that we had a memorable time. The overall atmosphere was cozy and inviting, making it the perfect spot for a family outing or a casual get-together with friends.

If you find yourself in Al Khobar, I wholeheartedly recommend paying a visit to Harat Ward.
